{"tid":320532,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好憎d仆街成日燒野燒衣？","createTime":"2017-07-13T14:52:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-20T18:48:54.000Z","uid":115758,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"747b1f84b3a3d24e4f233d419d7af925d74a262c","tid":320532,"uid":115758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:52:14.000Z","msg":"我住嗰度，有一戶賤種成日三更半夜凌晨嚮樓下燒野燒衣，每個禮拜都燒，唔知係拜神定乜鳩，令到啲衣隨風飄散，搞撚到污煙漳氣，同埋我住低層，佢嗰啲燒完既廢氣，升撚晒上嚟，打開咗隻窗，就搞撚到我成屋都係煙味。晾衫未乾掛嚮窗嘅都比佢搞到成陣煙味。<br />\n<br />\n到底有咩方法可以收呢d成日要拜神燒野既賤種皮？其實佢當街當巷燒野，算唔算係縱火？ 佢燒到啲火光好撚勁，唔係燒少少。<br />\n<br />\n最大問題係佢燒完搞到成地灰燼，啲大廈出入都要避撚左佢。再加上依家大熱天時，見到佢燒野真係人都燥！屌佢老母臭閪，鬼唔望佢死全家，到時我燒返野比佢冚家剷！"},{"pid":"c050c369e699cc1c8f2b766aa4842f6acd92ad8f","tid":320532,"uid":8246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:54:05.000Z","msg":"你肯定係人燒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"913b0d629aa5c19d5f93e5c4449d79e4c02e2ab8","tid":320532,"uid":103405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:58:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你肯定係人燒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"375a4272241c5e8ab868782a20f28ff639c5fed5","tid":320532,"uid":54481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:59:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你肯定係人燒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8456ccf5ff48adf9408aeb6165603369b6b9a4d","tid":320532,"uid":104758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T14:59:35.000Z","msg":"呢d人捉去坐監就岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d36d0f086ab4f7da7fcda37a5f1cdcdc006ba270","t